$Id: TODO,v 1.107 2015/09/15 03:16:44 zlb Exp $

- Allow importing meshes using user-defined comms:
     1. add a member comm_world to GRID, which is used to replace the global
	variable phgComm whenever applicable, e.g. in phgCreateComm_ (need to
	add an extra argument 'comm_world' to it)
     2. change phgImport to phgImport0 with an extra argument 'comm':
	. BOOLEAN phgImport0(GRID *g, const char *filename, BOOLEAN distr,
				MPI_Comm comm);
	. Add an internal static variable 'comm_world' which is initialized to
	  MPI_COMM_NULL, used to store the comm set through phgImportSetComm
	. #define phgImport(g, fn, dist) phgImport0(g, fn, dist, MPI_COMM_NULL)
	. #define phgImportSetComm(comm)  phgImport0(NULL, NULL, FALSE, comm)

- add the mode 'PHG_ASSEMBLED' to MAT and remove the member 'assembled'
  (add the 'mode' member to VEC?)

- Use 'INT' for the counts and disps in phgAlltoallv to allow large messages
  and remove the assertions "xxxx <= INT_MAX" in src/*.c.

- Implement a function for extracting components of a multi-dimensional DOF

- Add a 'type' member to DOF_TYPE to support INT-valued DOFs (do the same for
  MAT and VEC?).

- solver-ams.c: implement aux spaces for hp elements.

- utils.c: allow combined boundary types in bcmap file using '|'

- Reimplement caching (use separate caches for vertex/edge/face/elem bases?)
  for speeding up numerical quadrature of h-p bases.

- Periodicity support in the following functions:
	phgSurfaceCut, phgDupGrid

- Use communication instead of extrapolation for DOF interpolation
  when one child is missing (coarsen.c).

  Tests:
  mpirun -np 1 ./hp_test -default_dof_type DG4 -pre_refines=3 -post_refines=6
  mpirun -np 4 ./hp_test -default_dof_type DG4 -pre_refines=3 -post_refines=6
  mpirun -np 4 ./hp_test -default_dof_type DG4 -pre_refines=3 -post_refines=6 \
        -partitioner zoltan -zoltan_method random

- Add an optional pointer to the function computing element matrix/vector to
  MAT/VEC, and allow MAT/VEC/SOLVER to live through refinement, coarsening,
  and redistribution.

- Add codes for treating the case nvec > 0 in MAT/VEC/SOLVER.

- Optimize communications: design collective communication functions which
  only require local data lengths (use MPI_Probe to discover data lengths)

- Restart file
